Source: libevfibers
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Konstantin Olkhovskiy <lupus@oxnull.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), cmake, libev-dev, libvrb0-dev, valgrind,
 uthash-dev, check
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Section: libs
Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/libevfibers
Vcs-Browser: http://code.google.com/p/libevfibers/source/browse

Package: libevfibers-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libevfibers0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Small C fibers library --- development files
 Small c fiber library that uses libev based event loop and libcoro based
 coroutine context switching. as libcoro alone is barely enough to do something
 useful, this project aims at building a complete fiber api around it while
 leveraging libev's high performance and flexibility.

Package: libevfibers0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Small C fibers library --- runtime files
 Small c fiber library that uses libev based event loop and libcoro based
 coroutine context switching. As libcoro alone is barely enough to do something
 useful, this project aims at building a complete fiber api around it while
 leveraging libev's high performance and flexibility.
